Package: RippleR
Title: Spatial Ripple Analysis for Giotto and Xenium Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Yee Hoon",
      family = "Foong",
      email = "yeehoon.foong@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description:
    Provides tools for tumor-centered concentric-circle analysis
    of spatial transcriptomics data. Functions support generation
    of concentric circles, spatial radius annotation, peritumoral
    region labeling, visualization, and radius-based gene expression
    analysis for Giotto and Xenium objects.
